Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他知道马可也参加了歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有新情报来了我会告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大总统辅佐就像是做人质一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:01:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果乐观点看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:02:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁机在大总统睡觉的时候取下他的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大佐的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡还在到处转悠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我伊修瓦尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}520先士的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊修瓦尔发生了那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的事情都告诉了我这样的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,链金术师是追求真理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不知道身边的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐在想达成目的之后的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达成目的之后…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔 你恢复原来的身体后想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 想吃温莉的苹果派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脑子里已经塞满了恢复原来的身体这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先跟婆婆还有师傅打招呼 告诉他们“回来了”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 一直受她们照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会笑着迎接我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到大家的笑脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然情况很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有好消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的链金术无法发动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一个时间 地上似乎也无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个小女孩和斯卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他们能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的链金术里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我们不知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还没完全走到死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了？那个豆丁女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天一大早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 她说去哪了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整个中央都市？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且完全没有线索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送就送那种有很多美女照片的杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们离开的期间里 可别偷懒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去品尝一下西部的著名料理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大后要变强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我离开的期间里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利曹长 好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔蔓准尉 还没有出发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来向大佐还东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中央都市的勤务时间真是短暂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曹长是南方司令部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方司令部一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利曹长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 期待再见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来取忘记的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡好像还在中央都市里晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可得小心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且技术好的护卫已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你操劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我跟错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你认为错了就一枪毙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那天的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在允许的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉可真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的时候可不要偷懒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是兴趣增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我很光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脑子不好 进士官学校可是费了很大的劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您希望 会一直跟您到地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇后也被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 将军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是这种猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在寻找带着这家伙的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（你知道吗 知道的话请告诉我）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那边那个异类就放一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 没有黑白猫的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许已经不在中央都市了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 清的链丹术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也问问别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是不想欠大佐人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说起欠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好前面 前面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少 500先士？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,520先士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想糊弄过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这么精打细算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可成不了大人物的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是继续借着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等大佐做了大总统之后再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克爱中尉 还有伊修瓦尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱就算一直借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让你还给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到那个时候会再问你借零钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说等实行民主制了再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个也还了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再借一次 定个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 我必须活得相当久才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 别让中尉再担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你送我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精神 瓦涅莎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 罗伊小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 耶诞节夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了提提精神来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为病刚好 酒不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一个特别的 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉曼阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位名叫耶诞节夫人的女性从中央都市打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 别把极密线路的号码告诉普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我还没被抛弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指名要我这老头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护好少主
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是这副样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算被姚家选上的守护一族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道廉耻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…手臂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和兰芳的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给她介绍机械铠技师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的好意我们心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不需要进一步的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机械铠技师我们自己会想办法找的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人看到了兰芳的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再把你们的熟人卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了您 孙女的性命保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是个被人感谢的医生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺克斯医生 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没好到把麻烦一直留在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下的身体状况似乎在恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快夺回少主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着长生不老之法回国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等着 魔窟的住人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.01,0:13:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会忘记你的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺克斯医生 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 装成医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我这么个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 父亲 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 还精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有重要的事来到附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是瘦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是瘦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还是老样子对着尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这周治疗了两个活着的患者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然去救助人命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我现在以医生为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道父亲自伊修瓦尔以来一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 父亲也没有放弃做医生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢作为医生的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做得不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯咖啡再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱得一塌糊涂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 趁你父亲泡咖啡的时候 我们收拾一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真有神存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和家人一起喝咖啡这点幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是可以拥有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样伊修瓦尔就完全进入国军的管辖了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 金普利少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视等价交换 实现了超越想像的链成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细情况写成文书后提交
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头还给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这样知道贤者之石所在的只有你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被释放了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你杀了五个士官却没被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使了什么招？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我的人望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑死人了 炸弹狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然释放你这种发狂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的人到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.09,0:17:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长时间受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我取下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊的玩具 送给你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你出狱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你们的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说会给我工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得马可医生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作了贤者之石的研究者吧 我记得他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个马可也许
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有完全确定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看门的合成兽少了一头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可是擅长生物链成的链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也许是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更麻烦的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能和伊修瓦尔人斯卡一起逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为实行了伊修瓦尔歼灭战的红莲之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我手下漏掉的伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可原谅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现斯卡杀死也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是马可要带来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了这点事把我叫出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抓住了马可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以儆效尤 毁掉一座城市给他看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的工作吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会做肮脏的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来能用上这久违的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要毁灭一个城市 那个或许不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？又用了伊修瓦尔人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是马克医生的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直研究着石头的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么放我走？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个叫金普利的链金术师之事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长留下的研究书里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我无法理解的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究书？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长临死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这个国家的链金术很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这点 应该有记载
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是优秀的链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家的链金术 很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人 那个女孩回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡先生 您没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴增加了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他名叫马可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是制作贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.56,0:21:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助伊修瓦尔歼灭战的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石是？长生不老的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马可先生 你知道石头的制作方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做的？请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不要追求那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只破坏了脸的表面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他止血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.77,0:22:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸还是破坏得看不出是你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs60}（不要紧吗 马可先生）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我藏了兄长的研究书之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.35,0:22:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏着的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和微笑一同出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的火苗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降临在错综的中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.15,0:24:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第32话 大总统的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.94,0:24:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道反而会比较幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:27.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因为我犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:31.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}轻微的颤抖着  control过了还在颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:35.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太阳也好  运气（月亮）也罢  完全与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:36.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}“只有硬上了吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:39.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我这样劝说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:45.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情况很糟糕  临阵逃脱又没毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:49.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}虽然前途未卜  也只能靠胆量获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:52.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}压制着冲动  寻找敌我之间的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:55.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是胜利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能尝下胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下满腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二择其一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:10.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操纵命运的轮盘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:15.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}绝好的黄金时间  亲自把握机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:19.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}摆出一副扑克脸  设下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:24.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敌人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:31.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}无尽的pressure game  跨越过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:35.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}为了跨越荣耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:39.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代价？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:44.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底舍不得放弃哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.36,0:22:38.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:45.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:48.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}谈话直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:51.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}牵手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.12,0:22:56.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就这样明天后天也一直这样形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:23:00.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看着街上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:06.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个人是无法找到温暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.27,0:23:11.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道爱原来可以如此坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:17.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在与你相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:22.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一轮又一轮后依然想在此相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:28.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了不再走散而紧紧牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:33.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为一个人无法入睡  也无法做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:39.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在不安无法到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:44.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是没有星星的夜晚也要继续将其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的话能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:49.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}一个人无法走过的道路  如果是两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼着歌走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.93,0:23:56.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福

